{"tid":661129,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「人肉洗衣機」安全桿突鬆開 母女飛墮一死一傷","createTime":"2018-05-11T09:44:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-11T09:51:24.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c81b22ff25696a7594d83a3d249f80d2c4c98118","tid":661129,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T09:44:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180511/20387796\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180511%2F20387796&d=u5qNS%2BofXBNJlJje3acABJzN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=7da0b3c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180511%2F20387796&h=d813dc0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180511/20387796</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月11日 <br />\n<br />\n「人肉洗衣機」安全桿突鬆開<br />\n母女飛墮一死一傷<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n墨西哥瓜納華托（Guanajuato）一個嘉年華遊樂場發生駭人意外，一個機動遊戲升至半空時，其中一節座位的安全欄突然鬆開，一對母女從10米高墮下，造成一死一傷。<br />\n<br />\n從影片看到，機動遊戲猶如洗衣機滾筒般旋轉，現場傳來人們玩遊戲時的刺激的尖叫聲。機動遊戲升至最高點時，其中一節座位的安全欄突鬆脫，一名女子在半空被甩出機動遊戲，然後另一人隨即也從高處墮下，情景嚇人。<br />\n<br />\n50歲母親阿爾巴蘭(Irma Sanchez Albarran)陳屍地上，她當場證實死亡；她的女兒桑切斯(Nayeli Morales Sanchez)受重傷，要留醫深切治療部。<br />\n<br />\n事發時，這個一年一度的嘉年華僅開幕3天。當局正調查事件，暫沒有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日鏡報》  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n奇趣Pop：帶棕熊去街食雪糕有排煩<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n【今日笑一笑】R頭爽爆　化身煲水貓"},{"pid":"86a1670adaf5d963bc8323ede3b7d2963eeb84e5","tid":661129,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T09:45:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"176b2cac405d4c384edd234bb93588b6afb4290d","tid":661129,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T09:51:24.000Z","msg":"RIP"}]}